1
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:36,979
Yamamoto-san.

2
00:01:37,520 --> 00:01:38,720
Your Excellency Ito.

3
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:43,780
Did you sleep well last night?

4
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:50,660
It seems Your Excellency Ito is not very satisfied.

5
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:55,520
If you could be given

6
00:01:55,520 --> 00:01:57,520
a woman like Hu Linglong,

7
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:00,460
you would like her, wouldn't you?

8
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:04,000
Hahaha.

9
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,440
Yoshi.

10
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:08,400
Our war with the Chinese now

11
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,000
is on the verge of breaking out.

12
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:11,060
Besides military,

13
00:02:11,200 --> 00:02:12,440
we also need to control

14
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:13,900
their economic lifeline.

15
00:02:14,040 --> 00:02:15,080
I must win

16
00:02:15,760 --> 00:02:16,880
the tea export.

17
00:02:17,640 --> 00:02:19,300
Mr. Ito, please rest assured.

18
00:02:30,440 --> 00:02:31,170
Little girl.

19
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:32,170
Little girl.

20
00:02:36,400 --> 00:02:38,480
This is the tea workshop my father used when he was alive.

21
00:02:38,480 --> 00:02:40,360
Although it's been abandoned for many years,

22
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,560
I've cleaned it up.

23
00:02:42,079 --> 00:02:44,210
It's perfect for improving black tea.

24
00:02:44,720 --> 00:02:45,320
By the way,

25
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,400
yesterday,

26
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,460
I forgot to ask you.

27
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:50,160
Why did you suddenly want to improve black tea?

28
00:02:50,160 --> 00:02:51,520
You saw the ugly faces

29
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,880
of those British merchants.

30
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,800
Foreign tea is constantly improving its technology

31
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:56,200
and techniques.

32
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:58,760
But our Keemun black tea remains stagnant.

33
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:00,220
If this continues,

34
00:03:00,320 --> 00:03:01,720
it will only be a dead end.

35
00:03:02,160 --> 00:03:03,120
Historically,

36
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:06,000
Keemun black tea did undergo several improvements,

37
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,280
which is why it has been passed down to modern times

38
00:03:07,280 --> 00:03:08,680
and continues to thrive.

39
00:03:09,160 --> 00:03:11,960
My time travel changed Hu Linglong's life.

40
00:03:12,200 --> 00:03:15,160
If it causes the failure of the black tea improvement,

41
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:16,490
the future related to it

42
00:03:16,640 --> 00:03:17,880
should also change.

43
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:21,240
It seems I must do my best to make this happen.

44
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,600
Little girl,

45
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:24,400
what are you thinking about?

46
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:26,560
I'm not a little girl.

47
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:27,680
I have a name.

48
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:28,680
I'm Qiao Xin.

49
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:30,440
Qiao as in Qiaomu.

50
00:03:30,440 --> 00:03:31,320
Xin as in Xinxi.

51
00:03:31,920 --> 00:03:33,120
Qiao Xin.

52
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:35,490
That's a very nice name.

53
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:37,680
Oh.

54
00:03:38,040 --> 00:03:39,600
I was just thinking,

55
00:03:40,600 --> 00:03:42,600
since I also know something about tea,

56
00:03:42,600 --> 00:03:44,320
I should be able to help.

57
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,079
Moreover,

58
00:03:45,079 --> 00:03:47,040
when I occupied your body today,

59
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:49,860
I found that my sense of smell had recovered.

60
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:52,440
But wasn't it...

61
00:03:53,200 --> 00:03:54,360
It should be

62
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:56,240
because of the medicine Hu Wenyi gave you.

63
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:56,720
However,

64
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:57,840
we don't have time now

65
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:58,840
to look into this.

66
00:03:59,160 --> 00:04:00,640
The most important thing right now

67
00:04:00,640 --> 00:04:02,480
is to improve Keemun black tea.

68
00:04:10,120 --> 00:04:10,980
Yamamoto-san.

69
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:11,930
Hu Wenyi is here.

70
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,240
Mr. Yamamoto.

71
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,240
Sit.

72
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:29,680
Okay.

73
00:04:34,240 --> 00:04:35,200
Mr. Yamamoto.

74
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:36,400
I wonder

75
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:38,600
the girl I sent over a couple of days ago,

76
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:40,170
are you satisfied with her?

77
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:41,880
Hahaha.

78
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,480
Satisfied.

79
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:47,760
But such a woman who is easy to get

80
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,440
is ultimately boring.

81
00:04:50,040 --> 00:04:50,920
Ah.

82
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,000
It would be interesting

83
00:04:54,000 --> 00:04:55,880
to have a woman like Hu Linglong.

84
00:04:56,440 --> 00:04:57,970
That would be interesting.

85
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:01,120
So,

86
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:03,240
Mr. Yamamoto means

87
00:05:03,880 --> 00:05:05,080
to keep Hu Linglong?

88
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:07,400
No.

89
00:05:10,320 --> 00:05:11,360
Mr. Hu,

90
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,280
have you ever hunted?

91
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:16,240
Well...

92
00:05:17,800 --> 00:05:19,840
Please enlighten me, Mr. Yamamoto.

93
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,360
Hahaha.

94
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:26,160
After a hunter catches his prey,

95
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:29,200
it's only interesting

96
00:05:29,680 --> 00:05:31,000
if he can play with it.

97
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:33,600
I see.

98
00:05:34,159 --> 00:05:34,720
I see.

99
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:37,640
Hahaha.

100
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:40,480
Please.

101
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,520
Mr. Hu,

102
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:45,520
I mentioned the secret recipe for black tea before.

103
00:05:45,520 --> 00:05:47,180
How about this, Mr. Yamamoto.

104
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:48,800
In a few days,

105
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,560
I'll send you some

106
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:53,120
beautiful girls.

107
00:05:53,240 --> 00:05:54,159
Is that okay?

108
00:05:54,159 --> 00:05:55,360
Yoshi.

109
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:59,680
With the support of our Great Japanese Empire,

110
00:05:59,680 --> 00:06:01,240
you can do whatever you want.

111
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:02,160
I understand.

112
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:04,040
I understand.

113
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,280
Then

114
00:06:11,840 --> 00:06:13,040
I will take my leave.

115
00:07:09,920 --> 00:07:11,720
To my dear brother Zhinian,

116
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:13,960
The Japanese army has been making frequent moves lately,

117
00:07:13,960 --> 00:07:15,880
intending to tear apart our maritime borders.

118
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:17,610
The clouds of war are imminent.

119
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:20,000
The position of Captain is no longer a sinecure.

120
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,480
The naval guns are ready to fire;

121
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,280
how can we stand idly by?

122
00:07:23,440 --> 00:07:25,040
You carry the ambitions of youth

123
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:27,560
and should go to Weihaiwei to defend our borders together.

124
00:07:27,560 --> 00:07:28,640
With the national grudge on our shoulders,

125
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:30,640
I hope you will settle your family affairs as soon as possible

126
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:32,880
and come to save the situation with me.

127
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:36,760
Zhinian,

128
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,720
if you receive this letter,

129
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,450
can you come to me immediately?

130
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,840
I have something to say to you.

131
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:43,800
Okay,

132
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:45,360
I promise you.

133
00:07:54,960 --> 00:07:57,560
Improving this black tea is really difficult.

134
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:59,760
After studying it for days,

135
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,820
I finally made some progress.

136
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,440
Who

137
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,440
is this person?

138
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:56,240
What is he spilling?

139
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,160
Oh no.

140
00:09:01,400 --> 00:09:02,800
Hu Linglong is in danger.

141
00:09:02,920 --> 00:09:03,650
Hu Linglong!

142
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,580
Wake up, there's a bad guy.

143
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,120
Hu Linglong!

144
00:09:12,360 --> 00:09:13,000
Wake up!

145
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,120
There's a bad guy.

146
00:09:17,320 --> 00:09:18,160
Hu Linglong!

147
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:21,400
This person must be up to no good.

148
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:23,240
But Hu Linglong is currently

149
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:24,360
unconscious.

150
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:26,600
If I forcefully occupy her body,

151
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:28,650
I don't know how long I can last.

152
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:31,600
No.

153
00:09:31,600 --> 00:09:33,000
There's no time to think.

154
00:09:33,120 --> 00:09:34,440
My body feels so heavy.

155
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:46,760
Fire! Somebody help!

156
00:09:53,520 --> 00:09:54,160
Linglong!

157
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,560
Wake up, Hu Linglong!

158
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:17,290
Hu Linglong!

159
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:18,920
Linglong!

160
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:29,440
Long'er.

161
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:30,440
Long'er.

162
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:32,400
Long'er.

163
00:10:33,960 --> 00:10:34,640
Long'er.

164
00:10:35,120 --> 00:10:36,380
You're finally awake.

165
00:10:36,480 --> 00:10:37,080
Mother.

166
00:10:37,160 --> 00:10:39,220
Do you feel uncomfortable anywhere?

167
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:43,480
Mother.

168
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:46,020
I want to get up and sit for a while.

169
00:10:46,520 --> 00:10:47,040
Okay.

170
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,080
Put your shoes on.

171
00:10:57,920 --> 00:10:59,760
You were unconscious for a day and a night.

172
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:01,320
I was terrified.

173
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,080
Here.

174
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,400
It's good that you're fine.

175
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:07,930
It's good that you're fine.

176
00:11:10,000 --> 00:11:10,480
Here.

177
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,480
Take another sip.

178
00:11:16,160 --> 00:11:16,960
Mother.

179
00:11:17,880 --> 00:11:19,440
Did Zhinian save me?

180
00:11:20,920 --> 00:11:21,800
Yes.

181
00:11:22,400 --> 00:11:23,600
Thanks to Zhinian,

182
00:11:23,760 --> 00:11:25,490
he saved you from the teahouse.

183
00:11:26,200 --> 00:11:27,040
Otherwise,

184
00:11:28,160 --> 00:11:30,120
how could I live alone?

185
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:32,840
Mother.

186
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:35,760
The teahouse caught fire at night.

187
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:38,280
Why was Zhinian there?

188
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:40,920
I forgot to ask.

189
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:43,120
I will call Zhinian over today.

190
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:45,440
I will let him talk to you himself.

191
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:49,080
I'll go decoct another bowl of medicine for you.

192
00:11:49,080 --> 00:11:50,480
Lie down and rest first.
